    {
        "content": "<p>It's because of <code>b</code> occurs in the goal and you rewrite it's type there's a change the goal will not typecheck anymore, so to be safe it gets duplicated. The reason <code>simp</code> doesn't do this sometimes is probably that it keeps track of if the transformation is defeq (if actually only <code>dsimp</code> would have done the same thing) and since everything is definitional it knows it doesn't have to make a new variable.</p>",
        "id": 557899851,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1763463956
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Thanks Aaron. So are you saying that any time one does a <code>rw [...] at h</code> and <code>h</code> appears in the goal, this will happen?</p>",
        "id": 557920406,
        "sender_full_name": "Yannick Seurin",
        "timestamp": 1763469519
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>yes, that's correct</p>",
        "id": 557929099,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1763471345
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>and not just the goal, but anywhere</p>",
        "id": 557929135,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1763471357
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>so it could be because it's used in the type of another hypothesis, or in the value of a local let-decl</p>",
        "id": 557929252,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1763471389
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>OK, thanks! I don't think I've seen this explained anywhere, might be worth an addition to <code>rewrite</code> documentation.</p>",
        "id": 557943223,
        "sender_full_name": "Yannick Seurin",
        "timestamp": 1763474824
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It's not specific to <code>rewrite</code>, there's a function <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Lean.MVarId.replaceLocalDecl#doc\">docs#Lean.MVarId.replaceLocalDecl</a> and all the tactics that use this function in their implementation will show the same behavior</p>",
        "id": 557988738,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1763484219
    }
]